FBIS4-12838 "drnes072_k_94003" FBIS-NES-94-072 Daily Report 14 Apr 1994 IRAQ Clandestine Radio Comments Clandestine Radio Comments NC1404145194 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi People in Arabic 1400 GMT 14 Apr 94 NC1404145194 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi People Arabic BFN [Summary from poor reception] "Reports emerging from Baghdad" have said that something is wrong with "the dictator of Iraq Saddam Husayn." He has not appeared in public for some time. "The tyrant might be afflicted with a dangerous disease that has forced him to be confined to his bed. A group of doctors is attempting to cure him of fits of (?madness). Citizens have noticed that Baghdad Television is showing shots of old occasions, which has raised doubts about what is happening to the tyrant recently."
